description: A ciscoHealthMonNotification is sent if the measured
utilization has crossed the threshold value. It will be generated
when the value rises above the threshold. ciscoHealthMonShelfId and
ciscoHealthMonAddress are optional entries. This entry is valid only
if the notification generated for the monitoring types set on the
router shelf. This entry will not have anything if notification is
generated for the monitoring types set on the system controller.

event.Summary: Measured utilization $v4 is currently at value $v5 and has crossed the threshold value $v6

objects.test: $SNMPTRAPCMD CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonNotification CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonStatusType i 1 CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonShelfId i 9999 CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonAddress a 192.0.2.1 CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonDescr s EXAMPLE CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonValue u 99  CISCO-5800-HEALTH-MON-MIB::ciscoHealthMonThreshold i 99
